snippet.title: Superguy and Megaboy | Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the demo at https://gamejolt.com/games/superguymegaboy/918891

SAGE Booth: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/superguy-and-megaboy-wip-demo.2141/

My website: http://ethanwakegames.com

Superguy and Megaboy is a 2.75D free-roam superhero game I started developing a few years ago. I've hit several hiccups along the way, so I'm happy to finally release a demo! Feedback, constructive critisism and suggestions for improvement are welcome.

#sageexpo2024 #sage2024 #superhero #freeroam #openworld #gaming #pc #gamemaker
